{
  "stem": "753.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--if you can try that, come [BACKROUND NOISE] and, please, just help us when they enter--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--to enter so quietly that nobody will hear them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Thanks.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bye-bye.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, much later in life, I realized that I was one of those hidden children that had to live in plain sight.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only thing I ever had to hide was my identity and my Jewishness.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were moments in those days that I was-- I wished secretly that they would find us, put us on a train, and that finally I could be myself, tell the truth who I am, open up, and not live in this constant anxiety.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was-- fear was a constant companion.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was an emotion that was always with us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I never-- because I felt a tremendous responsibility because I was the spokesman all the time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I had to grow up so fast and become an adult, behave like an adult and behave like-- be a responsible person, although I looked like a child.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Definitely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew that if we are caught by the Germans, this is the end.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, we, we either got executed right away, shot, or put on a train or going-- [LAUGHS] we knew already where we are supposed to go and where we are supposed to be as Jews.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And another thing was we felt responsible for those people that were shielding us, like this priest.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When I think back, I mean, this was a tremendous responsibility and tremendous thing from a, a, a man to trust a child not to speak.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because don't forget, these are years when you-- secrecy for an adolescent is a very hard thing to live with.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, I was sometimes tempted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Oh, I have to find somebody to confide.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
